name: Aquarium Controller Eagle Schematics
tagline: All info for Lighting Control Module
body:
### Welcome the Aquarium Controller Eagle Schematics.
Feel free to check out all the schematics and board layouts for items designed for the Arduino/Raspberry Pi aquarium controller.  Everything is open source and free for use.

Check out the GitHub repository!
http://github.com - automatic!
[GitHub](https://github.com/JaredMRomano/AquariumController.EagleSchematics)

### Authors and Contributors
I, @JaredMRomano am the creator of the Arduino/Raspberry Pi Aquarium Controller, feel free to contact me with any issues or questions, but keep in mind, this is a side project and not my primary job.  I would also love help and fellow contributors, so if you have an idea let me know!

### Terms of Use
All sources are free and free to use in other projects, however I am still learning, therefore there is no warranty or official support. Thanks and enjoy.
